<html lang="ru">
<head>

<style>

table {
  font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, sans-serif;
  width: 90%;
  font-size: 200%;
  margin: auto;
}

caption {
  text-align: center;
  font-weight: bold;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 15px;
  font-size: 150%;

}

thead {
  background: #FAE86E;
  color: black;
}

thead th {
  background: #FAE86E;
}

th,
td {
  padding: 5px 10px;
}


tfoot {
  background: #43914F;
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 110%;
}

tfoot th {
  background: #43914F;
}

tfoot tr th:last-child {
}

</style>

</head>
<body>
<table>
  <caption>%TITLE%</caption>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th align="center" width="100%" colspan="3">%CAPTION%</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
    </tr>
      <td>
        <p align="center">%DESC%<br>
        <span style="font-size: 150%">%INFO%</span><p align="center">    

        <img src="data:image/png;base64, %QR%" alt="QR code" >

        <!--OK        
        <img alt="OK" src="data:image/png;base64,">
        OK-->       
        <!--FAIL  
        <img alt="FAIL" src="data:image/png;base64,">
        FAIL-->          
        <!--WAIT             
        <img alt="WAIT" src="data:image/png;base64,">
        WAIT-->      
        <!--INFO        
        <img alt="INFO" src="data:image/png;base64,">
        INFO-->        
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
  <tfoot>
    <tr>
      <th colspan="2">%OPERATION%</th>
    </tr>
  </tfoot>
</table>
</body>
